mean_en: a very small piece of matter (\u003d a substance) with a positive electric charge that forms part of the nucleus (\u003d central part) of an atom
sentence: Protons are positively charged particles in the center of an atom.
sentence_trans: 质子是原子核中带正电的粒子。
